</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="75.[1382,2590,3314,3471]" lastBlockId="76.[786,1379,269,695]" lastPageId="76" lastPageNumber="834" pageId="75" pageNumber="833">
Form hwmeralis has been treated as a species and a subspecies of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Thomas" authorityYear="1901" box="[2315,2440,3393,3426]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Glauconycteris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="75" pageNumber="833" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="beatrix">G. beatrix</taxonomicName>
. Here it is treated as distinct from 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Thomas" authorityYear="1901" box="[1717,1838,3432,3465]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Glauconycteris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="75" pageNumber="833" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="beatrix">G. beatrix</taxonomicName>
, pending revision ofits taxonomic status. A. Hassanin and colleagues in 2018 retrieved 
<taxonomicName authorityName="J. A. Allen" authorityYear="1917" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Glauconycteris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="76" pageNumber="834" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="humeralis">G. humeralis</taxonomicName>
as possibly polyphyletic, with partsister to a clade including G. atra, G. 
<taxonomicName authorityName="J. A. Allen" authorityYear="1917" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Glauconycteris" isUncertain="true" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="76" pageNumber="834" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="humeralis">cf. humeralis</taxonomicName>
, and G. 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Thomas" authorityYear="1901" box="[950,1078,395,420]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Glauconycteris" isUncertain="true" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="76" pageNumber="834" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="beatrix">cf. beatrix</taxonomicName>
. Monotypic.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="76" pageNumber="834" type="distribution">
<caption ID-DOI="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6398093" ID-Zenodo-Dep="6398093" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6398093/files/figure.png" inLine="true" pageId="76" pageNumber="834" targetBox="[171,763,280,695]" targetPageId="76">
